2010-05-30 Hauke Hain  <hhpreuss@googlemail.com>

	* Added possibility to use the t3blog commenting interface. By default 
	  mm_forum_blog creates a mm_forum topic if the first comments is written.
	  If comments are immediately approved a post is created.
	  
	  Attention: The BE module "Comments" of t3blog is not supported at all!
	
2010-05-24 Hauke Hain  <hhpreuss@googlemail.com>

